2001-07-07  Paul Houghton  <paul.houghton@wcom.com>

	* Param.hh: changed arguments argXXX methods to include valueName,
	shortDesc, longDesc and required. For example:

	    Was: argStr( dest, "desc", "arg-id", "ENV_VAR" )
	    Now: argStr( dest,
			 "FILENAME",
			 "short desc",
			 "long_desc",
			 false,
			"arg-id",
			"ENV_VAR" )
	
	Note: still need to acutally use these new values.

